name: High-Knee March
step_by_step: March in place lifting knees to waist height

name: Karaoke (Crossover Steps)
step_by_step: Crossover step laterally down and back

name: Lateral Shuffle
step_by_step: Shuffle side to side in athletic stance

name: Arm Circles Forward & Back
step_by_step: Small to large arm circles forward, then backward

name: Cross-Body Arm Swings
step_by_step: Swing arms across chest, alternating top and bottom

name: Dynamic Lunges with Reach
step_by_step: Step into lunge, reach arms overhead, alternate legs

name: Opne gate into lateral lunge
step_by_step: Lift leg and open gate, land in lateral lunge

name: Walking Quad Pull
step_by_step: Walk forward pulling heel to glute

name: Walking Hamstring Floor Touches
step_by_step: Walk forward and swipe at ground each step

name: Inchworm
step_by_step: Hinge, walk hands to plank, walk feet in

name: Froggy Glute Bridge
step_by_step: Lie on back with knees out, drive hips up, squeeze glutes

name: Single-Leg Hamstring Kick to RDL
step_by_step: Kick leg forward, hinge into single-leg RDL

name: Standing V-Hamstring Stretch
step_by_step: Stand with legs apart, stretch down the middle, then each leg

name: Front Leg Swings
step_by_step: Swing leg forward and back while balancing

name: Side-to-Side Leg Swings
step_by_step: Swing leg side to side across body

name: Explosive Push-Up
step_by_step: Slow down on pushup, explosive on up part of pushop
